---
import "../styles/generel.css";
---

<section class="about">
  <div class="about-section__inner about-grid">
    <div class="about-left">
      <h1>
        MOTIV-
        <br />
        ATION
      </h1>
      <!-- <div class="about-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="/img/fist-outline.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div> -->
    </div>

    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        Astemon was born from a simple observation: Lisbon is full of people who
        want to do the right thing, but don’t always know how to.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong
          >Tourists, expats, and exchange students often arrive eager to live
          sustainably</strong
        >, only to find that the city’s waste sorting system feels confusing,
        fragmented, and mostly explained in Portuguese.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our motivation was to bridge that gap. We wanted to create a space where
        sustainability feels accessible, visual, and easy to understand, no
        matter where you come from.
      </p>

      <p>
        Astemon exists to turn everyday waste sorting into a shared act of care
        for the city we all call home, even if only for a while!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--ashbrown);
  }
  .about-section__inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3.25rem;
    padding-left: 0;
    padding-right: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 260px) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: "Lexend Giga", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-icon img {
    max-width: 180px;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-section__inner {
      padding-left: 3rem;
      padding-right: 3rem;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
